  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 12 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 1 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 11</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a head-sized sphere of fiery Chakra in front of your hands, and then fire it towards the area to deal 1d4 fire damage. If you wish to target a very small object or send the sphere through a small passage, you must make a ranged touch attack in order to hit it (it has a Defense of 5 + size modifiers). In that case, the sphere has a range increment of 10 ft and cannot exceed the technique's range.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> You can spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d4 (maximum 3d4).</p>\n\n",
